{"tid":532661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《絕地求生》中國玩家瘋狂開外掛 騰訊與警方已逮捕120餘人","createTime":"2018-01-18T05:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T13:01:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":99,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe7bcd0c4d73fd676bf6488ca69ab0ffb8805c8","tid":532661,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"由 Bluehole 公司研發的大逃殺類型線上遊戲《絕地求生》(PUBG)，上市以來一直面臨玩家使用外掛作弊的問題，而總監 Brendan Greene 更表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">99% 的外掛都來自中國</span>，這讓獲得中國代理權騰訊備感壓力，騰訊與警方合作，展現打擊外掛的決心。<br />\n<br />\n外掛製作和銷售集團兜售各式各樣的外掛，有人物透視、超準自瞄、無後座力、走路加速、超級子彈等，可分單項購買或是成套購買，銷售團隊一個月營業額可因此達到上百萬人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n網路追蹤網站 Steam Spy 數據顯示，《絕地求生》全球有超過 3000 萬的玩家，而其中中國約占了一半，這讓其他地區的玩家苦不堪言，卻沒辦法禁止中國玩家使用該遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n僅管騰訊一直致力打擊外掛製作業者，但諷刺的是，若進入前 10 名玩家排行榜，有 8 名玩家的名稱類似為「請連絡 QQ574352XXX」，他們透過騰訊旗下的通訊軟體 QQ 販售外掛。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊向玩家承諾，表示將通過法律和技術手段，給玩家打造一個綠色、公平的遊戲環境，截至 2017 年底為止，已與中國警方聯手破獲 30 起案子，逮捕犯罪嫌疑人 120 人。<br />\n<br />\n而網路遊戲反作弊系統 BattlEye，在 2017 年 12 月 28 日推文表示，在《絕地求生》上，已封鎖超過 150 萬筆作弊帳號，比起 11 月的封鎖帳號，成長一倍之於，公司表示，打擊作弊行為是一項不斷在進行的工作，問題永遠不會被根除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4018005/l/ce112d61fe4f444d5bb9d8248c0fab70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4018005%2Fl%2Fce112d61fe4f444d5bb9d8248c0fab70.jpg&h=526be7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBattlEye 表示封鎖帳號來到 150 萬<br />\n<br />\n而從每個月成長的新用戶來看，可以了解為甚麼 Bluehole 和騰訊如此致力於打擊作弊玩家，從去年 12 月到現在，共買出超過 510 萬組的《絕地求生》，但是每天的新玩家只增加 13.1 萬，代表充滿外掛的環境，會讓新玩家卻步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4018005/l/50fb79bbd096b3ab6da6f0d3e9d8b262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4018005%2Fl%2F50fb79bbd096b3ab6da6f0d3e9d8b262.jpg&h=280cb8af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新玩家數目與遊戲售出數目不相符<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4018005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4018005&d=yRN%2Fokt7E13NHUuX5ep%2Fq7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8feb8c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4018005</a>"},{"pid":"81366e553a252bee5ed9aa911ee2d4eefe523dd3","tid":532661,"uid":4661,"like":102,"dislike":2,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"多中國人既game一定唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b989fb9b113db12dec1f108ef8cf24089a6bbd","tid":532661,"uid":48234,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"共產黨出手管埋班東亞病夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">話緊你哋班外掛狗係東亞病夫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇外掛就唔撚識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"60f0a0ad26ca947ebed1c156e29e6fc56234a054","tid":532661,"uid":8347,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"99%外掛來自中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d977c080ab3067bf1c4eb49207554d82db7dc3","tid":532661,"uid":37735,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"f2b989fb9b113db12dec1f108ef8cf24089a6bbd","tid":532661,"uid":48234,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"共產黨出手管埋班東亞病夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\